headline: Wall Street Analysts Think Interactive Brokers (IBKR) Could Surge 25.57%: Read This Before Placing a Bet
summary: The mean of analysts' price targets for Interactive Brokers (IBKR) points to a 25.6% upside in the stock. While this highly sought-after metric has not proven reasonably effective, strong agreement among analysts in raising earnings estimates does indicate an upside in the stock.
